[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]A Solution to Help Scientifically Resolve Whiplash Cases in the UK [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]-
[normal] the pain syndrome can be fabricated itself, or
[normal]-
[normal] a mild pain syndrome can be consciously amplified.
